{"tid":295601,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［有片］睇馬賽太high，22歲正妹找男伴「騎馬」野戰，影片瘋傳全家都看過！","createTime":"2017-06-24T01:47:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-24T01:50:02.000Z","uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6814d6e8882afa16adb06ed80866347da0644e74","tid":295601,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T01:47:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=q3gUSeXIMc4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dq3gUSeXIMc4&d=V%2FzvkibrovXKhrUX6s6g7wRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=0ec80264\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=q3gUSeXIMc4</a><br />\n英國一對情侶突然「性致」來了，在賽馬場外一處草地上，以女上男下的「騎馬式」嘿咻，全程被拍下上傳，在網路上遭瘋傳。據了解，片中女主角事後向友人透露，全家人包含爺爺奶奶都看過這部影片了，讓她很崩潰，有家也不敢回。<br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報導，22歲髮型師桑柯（Marissa Sonkur）當時去看賽馬，跟男子一起喝了幾杯啤酒後，兩人天雷勾動地火，跑到一片空蕩的草地「開戰」，由她在上面主動「騎馬」。但是，男生的一名朋友偷偷跟在後面拍下過程，並且上傳到男生的聊天室，才流傳出去。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.ettoday.net/images/2614/d2614216.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2614%2Fd2614216.jpg&h=92b45e5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.ettoday.net/images/2614/d2614215.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2614%2Fd2614215.jpg&h=1c3b59bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.ettoday.net/news/20170623/951238.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20170623%2F951238.htm&d=V%2FzvkibrovXKhrUX6s6g7wRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=908b79b4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.ettoday.net/news/20170623/951238.htm</a>"},{"pid":"44771465ac9daf970b627712d536f41944f4f9e5","tid":295601,"uid":46454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T01:50:02.000Z","msg":"好想知道如果呢件事係呢幾日Royal Ascot期間,男女主角會唔會終身被blacklist <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}